WEBVTT

00:10.410 --> 00:11.611
The guy's name is adam.

00:12.012 --> 00:13.613
And you're going to
listen to what he has to say.

00:13.648 --> 00:15.615
This is a waste of time.

00:16.015 --> 00:17.582
No, it's not.

00:17.617 --> 00:19.219
My mother told
me all about him.

00:19.254 --> 00:20.785
He can help you.

00:20.820 --> 00:22.022
Mutant x is for real.

00:22.422 --> 00:23.989
Are you expecting me
to just go run and hide?

00:24.024 --> 00:26.226
Adam protects
new mutants like you
by bringing them to the

00:26.261 --> 00:28.428
underground where those
government goons can't find you.

00:28.463 --> 00:30.830
I can
take care of myself.

00:30.865 --> 00:31.997
Okay.

00:32.031 --> 00:34.034
And, i'm not about to
trust some guy i don't know.

00:34.434 --> 00:35.600
Marc, please.

00:35.635 --> 00:37.637
Just listen
to what he has to say.

00:37.672 --> 00:38.655
Sorry, babe.

00:38.690 --> 00:39.639
I'm outta here.

00:40.040 --> 00:40.840
No, no. No, no.
Please. Please.

00:40.875 --> 00:42.442
Please megan, let go of me.

00:42.477 --> 00:43.660
You can't leave.

00:43.695 --> 00:44.844
I said, let go.

00:44.879 --> 00:46.463
Megan.

00:46.498 --> 00:48.274
Marc.

00:48.309 --> 00:50.050
Megan!

00:52.000 --> 00:58.074
